---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import QuoteForm from '../../components/QuoteForm.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Results | 22 Local Marketing" description="Real before-and-afters from 22 Local Marketing clients. Site redesigns, ranking growth, and the receipts to back it up.">

<link slot="head" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Courier+Prime&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<!-- HERO -->
<header class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow-rugged">
      <span class="eb-dash"></span>
      <span>RESULTS</span>
      <span class="eb-sep">·</span>
      <span>RECEIPTS, NOT PROMISES</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-frame">
      <h1>Before, after, and <span class="accent">the receipts.</span></h1>
    </div>
    <p class="lead">Drag the slider on each case to see what we inherited and what we shipped. Then scroll through the receipts — rankings, GBP, dashboards, reviews.</p>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- STATS BAR -->
<section class="container">
  <div class="stats-bar">
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-label">Active clients</div>
      <div class="stat-value">12+</div>
      <div class="stat-desc">Home service operators across NC, FL, OH, and VA</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-label">Avg time to map pack</div>
      <div class="stat-value">90 days</div>
      <div class="stat-desc">From kickoff to top-3 ranking on a head term</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-label">Combined keywords ranking</div>
      <div class="stat-value">8,400+</div>
      <div class="stat-desc">Search terms our clients now appear for</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-label">Client retention</div>
      <div class="stat-value">94%</div>
      <div class="stat-desc">Past 18 months. Month-to-month, never locked-in</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FILTER -->
  <div class="filter-bar">
    <span class="filter-label">Filter</span>
    <button class="filter-btn active" data-filter="all">All</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="tree">Tree services</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="land">Land management</button>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ CASE 1: RANGER TREE CARE ============ -->
<section class="case-study" data-vertical="tree">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="case-head">
      <div>
        <div class="case-num">CASE 01 · TREE SERVICES</div>
        <h2 class="case-title">Ranger Tree Care</h2>
        <div class="case-meta">
          <span class="pill">Satellite Beach, FL</span>
          <span class="pill">9-month engagement</span>
          <span class="pill">Growth tier</span>
        </div>
        <div class="case-story">
          <p>Ranger came to us in <strong>May 2025</strong> leaning on HomeAdvisor, Thumbtack, and Yelp for leads while burning ad budget without a coherent strategy. The site was a single-pager. The GBP was unclaimed photos and three reviews. They were invisible on Google.</p>
          <p>We rebuilt the site, rebuilt the GBP, launched Google Ads from day one, and started shipping service + location pages on a weekly cadence. Nine months later they rank for <strong>over 1,000 queries</strong> and sit at <strong>#4 in Melbourne</strong> for the head term "Tree Care" — one position from the maps pack.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="case-side-stats">
        <div class="case-stat">
          <div class="case-stat-label">Impressions / 90d</div>
          <div class="case-stat-value">43.6K</div>
          <div class="case-stat-desc">Up from ~400 at start</div>
        </div>
        <div class="case-stat">
          <div class="case-stat-label">Keywords ranking</div>
          <div class="case-stat-value">1,000+</div>
          <div class="case-stat-desc">Up from 11 at start</div>
        </div>
        <div class="case-stat">
          <div class="case-stat-label">Maps rank · Melbourne</div>
          <div class="case-stat-value">#4</div>
          <div class="case-stat-desc">For head term "Tree Care"</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ba-section">
      <div class="ba-section-head">
        <h3>Site rebuild &middot; before / after</h3>
        <span class="hint">Drag the handle to reveal</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ba" data-ba>
        <div class="ba-img ba-before">
          <div class="site-mock">
            <div class="site-chrome">
              <div class="dots"><span class="r"></span><span class="y"></span><span class="g"></span></div>
              <div class="url">rangertreecare.com</div>
            </div>
            <div class="site-body site-before">
              <div class="old-logo">★ RANGER TREE CARE ★</div>
              <div class="old-tag">Tree Trimming &amp; Removal Since 2019!!!</div>
              <div class="old-marquee">★★★ CALL NOW FOR FREE QUOTE 24/7 ★★★</div>
              <div class="old-nav">Home | About | Services | Contact</div>
              <div class="old-body">
                <h2>Welcome to Our Website</h2>
                <p>We are a tree service company located in Satellite Beach FL. We do tree trimming, removal, stump grinding. Call us today!</p>
                <a class="old-cta">CLICK HERE</a>
              </div>
              <div class="old-footer">© 2019 — Hit counter: 1,247</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ba-img ba-after">
          <div class="site-mock">
            <div class="site-chrome">
              <div class="dots"><span class="r"></span><span class="y"></span><span class="g"></span></div>
              <div class="url">rangertreecare.com</div>
            </div>
            <div class="site-body site-after">
              <div class="after-nav">
                <span class="brand"><span class="brand-dot"></span>Ranger Tree Care</span>
                <span class="nav-links"><span>Services</span><span>Service Areas</span><span>About</span><span>Reviews</span></span>
                <span class="nav-cta">Free quote</span>
              </div>
              <div class="after-hero">
                <div class="after-hero-left">
                  <h1>Tree care done <span class="acc">right</span> in Melbourne.</h1>
                  <p>Trimming, removal, stump grinding, and 24-hour storm response across Brevard County.</p>
                  <span class="after-hero-cta">Get a free quote →</span>
                </div>
                <div class="after-hero-img"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="after-stats">
                <div class="after-stat"><div class="v">15+ yrs</div><div class="l">Local crew</div></div>
                <div class="after-stat"><div class="v">200+</div><div class="l">5-star reviews</div></div>
                <div class="after-stat"><div class="v">24/7</div><div class="l">Emergency</div></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ba-label before">Before</div>
        <div class="ba-label after">After</div>
        <div class="ba-handle"><div class="ba-grip"></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="car-section">
      <div class="car-section-head">
        <h3>The receipts &middot; rankings, GBP, dashboard, reviews</h3>
        <span class="car-counter" data-counter></span>
      </div>
      <div class="car" data-car>
        <div class="car-viewport">
          <div class="car-track">
            <div class="car-slide">
              <div class="car-slide-label">Google · "Tree Care Melbourne FL"</div>
              <div class="cs-serp">
                <div class="serp-bar">tree care melbourne fl</div>
                <div class="serp-result"><div class="domain">homeadvisor.com</div><div class="title">Top 10 Tree Services in Melbourne, FL · HomeAdvisor</div><div class="desc">Compare quotes from local tree service pros in Melbourne...</div></div>
                <div class="serp-result"><div class="domain">yelp.com</div><div class="title">Best Tree Services Near Melbourne, FL · Yelp</div><div class="desc">Find the best tree services in Melbourne with verified reviews...</div></div>
                <div class="serp-result featured"><div class="domain">rangertreecare.com</div><div class="title">Tree Care in Melbourne, FL · Ranger Tree Care</div><div class="desc">Trimming, removal, stump grinding, and storm response across Brevard County.</div></div>
                <div class="serp-result"><div class="domain">angi.com</div><div class="title">Tree Service Companies in Melbourne, FL</div><div class="desc">Get matched with top-rated tree services...</div></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="car-slide">
              <div class="car-slide-label">Google Business Profile</div>
              <div class="cs-gbp">
                <div class="cs-gbp-left">
                  <div class="gbp-name">Ranger Tree Care</div>
                  <div class="gbp-stars"><span class="stars">★★★★★</span><span class="num">4.9 · 218 Google reviews</span></div>
                  <div class="gbp-info">
                    <div class="gbp-info-row"><span class="ic">•</span><span>Tree service in Satellite Beach, FL</span></div>
                    <div class="gbp-info-row"><span class="ic">•</span><span>Open 24 hours · Emergency response</span></div>
                    <div class="gbp-info-row"><span class="ic">•</span><span>Serves Melbourne, Palm Bay, Cocoa, Vero Beach</span></div>
                    <div class="gbp-info-row"><span class="ic">•</span><span>Family-owned · Insured · Bonded</span></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="gbp-actions">
                    <span class="act primary">Call</span>
                    <span class="act">Directions</span>
                    <span class="act">Website</span>
                    <span class="act">Save</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="cs-gbp-photos">
                  <div class="ph"></div><div class="ph"></div><div class="ph"></div><div class="ph"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="car-slide">
              <div class="car-slide-label">Search Console · 12-month impressions</div>
              <div class="cs-chart">
                <h4>Search Console &middot; 12-month performance</h4>
                <div class="chart-meta">
                  <span>Total impressions <span class="v">43,612</span></span>
                  <span>Clicks <span class="v">2,184</span></span>
                  <span>Avg position <span class="v">8.4</span></span>
                </div>
                <svg class="chart-svg" viewBox="0 0 800 240" preserveAspectRatio="none">
                  <defs>
                    <linearGradient id="g1" x1="0" x2="0" y1="0" y2="1">
                      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#FB5607" stop-opacity="0.35"/>
                      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#FB5607" stop-opacity="0"/>
                    </linearGradient>
                  </defs>
                  <path d="M0,220 L60,218 L120,214 L180,205 L240,190 L300,170 L360,148 L420,118 L480,90 L540,70 L600,55 L660,42 L720,28 L800,22 L800,240 L0,240 Z" fill="url(#g1)"/>
                  <path d="M0,220 L60,218 L120,214 L180,205 L240,190 L300,170 L360,148 L420,118 L480,90 L540,70 L600,55 L660,42 L720,28 L800,22" fill="none" stroke="#FB5607" stroke-width="2.5"/>
                  <circle cx="800" cy="22" r="4" fill="#FB5607"/>
                </svg>
                <div class="chart-axis"><span>MAY '25</span><span>JUL</span><span>SEP</span><span>NOV</span><span>JAN '26</span><span>MAR</span></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="car-slide">
              <div class="car-slide-label">Reporting dashboard</div>
              <div class="cs-dashboard">
                <div class="panel"><div class="panel-label">Leads · 30d</div><div class="panel-value">82</div><div class="panel-delta">↑ 41% vs prev</div></div>
                <div class="panel"><div class="panel-label">Cost / lead</div><div class="panel-value">$38</div><div class="panel-delta">↓ 22% vs prev</div></div>
                <div class="panel"><div class="panel-label">Maps views</div><div class="panel-value">12,440</div><div class="panel-delta">↑ 18% vs prev</div></div>
                <div class="panel"><div class="panel-label">Calls · 30d</div><div class="panel-value">147</div><div class="panel-delta">↑ 33% vs prev</div></div>
                <div class="panel"><div class="panel-label">New reviews</div><div class="panel-value">24</div><div class="panel-delta">↑ 50% vs prev</div></div>
                <div class="panel"><div class="panel-label">Avg rating</div><div class="panel-value">4.9★</div><div class="panel-delta">218 total</div></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="car-slide">
              <div class="car-slide-label">Customer reviews</div>
              <div class="cs-reviews">
                <div class="rev">
                  <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                  <div class="quote">"Showed up the same day for a storm-damaged oak. Fair price, clean cleanup. Will call them again."</div>
                  <div class="author"><span class="av">JM</span><span>Jessica M. · Melbourne, FL</span></div>
                </div>
                <div class="rev">
                  <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                  <div class="quote">"Took down two 80-foot pines in our backyard. Crew was professional, careful around the fence."</div>
                  <div class="author"><span class="av">RT</span><span>Rick T. · Palm Bay, FL</span></div>
                </div>
                <div class="rev">
                  <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                  <div class="quote">"Best tree service in Brevard County. Honest quote, finished early, hauled everything away."</div>
                  <div class="author"><span class="av">DK</span><span>Danielle K. · Cocoa, FL</span></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="car-dots"></div>
        <div class="car-controls">
          <button class="car-btn car-prev" aria-label="Previous">←</button>
          <button class="car-btn car-next" aria-label="Next">→</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ CASE 2: FONVILLE TREE SERVICE ============ -->
<section class="case-study" data-vertical="tree">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="case-head">
      <div>
        <div class="case-num">CASE 02 · TREE SERVICES</div>
        <h2 class="case-title">Fonville Tree Service</h2>
        <div class="case-meta">
          <span class="pill">Wake Forest, NC</span>
          <span class="pill">2-year engagement</span>
          <span class="pill">Dominate tier</span>
        </div>
        <div class="case-story">
          <p>Fonville is the case study for what consistency over time looks like. They came on at the start of <strong>2024</strong> with a respectable site but barely any organic visibility. We pushed weekly content, monthly backlinks, and aggressive GBP work.</p>
          <p>Two years in, they're the answer for tree service across the Wake Forest / Raleigh / Durham triangle. <strong>500+ Google reviews</strong>, top-3 maps pack across 8 cities, and an organic pipeline that runs itself.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="case-side-stats">
        <div class="case-stat">
          <div class="case-stat-label">Google reviews</div>
          <div class="case-stat-value">500+</div>
          <div class="case-stat-desc">4.9 avg across the territory</div>
        </div>
        <div class="case-stat">
          <div class="case-stat-label">Map pack cities</div>
          <div class="case-stat-value">8</div>
          <div class="case-stat-desc">Top-3 for "tree service [city]"</div>
        </div>
        <div class="case-stat">
          <div class="case-stat-label">Organic share</div>
          <div class="case-stat-value">72%</div>
          <div class="case-stat-desc">Of monthly lead volume</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ba-section">
      <div class="ba-section-head">
        <h3>Site refresh &middot; before / after</h3>
        <span class="hint">Drag the handle to reveal</span>
      </div>
